metadata.name: GM Fam
metadata.description: In front of us is a cartoon blonde girl standing outside in the early morning hours. She is dressed in a white coat that nicely frames her figure. Her t-shirt has the phrase GM fam tweeted on it, which is a popular greeting to the Twitter NFT community. The girl looks straight ahead, as if expecting something interesting or wanting to start her day with new adventures. Her eyes sparkle with energy and cheerfulness, making it feel as if she is ready to overcome any obstacle as long as she has that energy. Overall, the drawing looks bright and emotional, making the viewer feel that the early morning could be the beginning of something great and exciting.
